author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of Poliça, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited the USB Forum at Minnesota Public Radio back in 2013.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Smug
00:04:08 Spilling Lines
00:07:14 Chain My Name
00:11:30 So Leave

Musicians
Channy Leaneagh – vocals
Drew Christopherson – drums, percussion
Chris Bierden – bass
Ben Ivascu – drums

Credits
Engineer – Mike DeMark, Maury Jensen
Producer – Lindsay Kimball
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
